summary: saw someone say that bts shouldn't win every award bc other fandoms will hate them and i was like ?? other fandoms already hate...
body:
saw someone say that bts shouldn’t win every award bc other fandoms will hate them and i was like ??

other fandoms already hate them, them winning more awards won’t change anything

everyone getting mad bts are getting this big when they haven’t done anything to make their faves even bigger

stop hating on bts and start paying more attention to your faves

of course, we want them to win every award they can what kind of fan wouldn’t want that?

of course, we want bts to get bigger than they are

do we like them getting hate? no, but we know its not their fault or ours

the hate comes from either jealous fans that want the same for their groups or idols but won’t do anything to achieve that so they just hate on bts for no reason at all other than them getting bigger and better or from xenophobic and racist people that cant stand bts being this popular just because they are Asian.

bts shall and will win more awards we don’t care about the hate, keep being bitter.

summary:
Echoes flowing through time
A single shot in the dark
I tried to take their pain and make it mine
But I couldn't save them with...
body:
Echoes flowing through time

A single shot in the dark

I tried to take their pain and make it mine

But I couldn’t save them with just my heart


Cycle after cycle of pain and regret

I’d watch as each attempt failed

I’d gone back to even before we’d met

But the seals on our coffins were already nailed


Wait…

No I can fix this!

There’s no time to waste

If I had been the one who jumped…

No,I won’t be missed

And yet…he’s been left behind

Another one forgotten…another soul defaced

summary: BTS reaction when they ask you to live with them
title: BTS reaction when they ask you to live with them
body:
*Note: Some may wonder why did it take so long if this isn’t long…well I don’t have an answer…or a schedule*

Jin-

Jin decided to move out of the dorm into his own apartment after the explosion of popularity with the group. He, of course being the oldest, wanted more space of his own. The two of you have been dating for more than a year now, coming on a strong second year of the relationship, and more than anything he wanted to share the space with you. “Jin, where are you taking me? Can I take off this blindfold now, this is a bit unnerving.” giggling you flail your arms out hoping not to bump into anything. “Where’s the trust Jagi?” he continues guiding you, where eventually he leads you to sit down. You feel his hands on your head and he restores your vision, blinking a couple of times you gasp at the dinner laid out for you. The centerpiece of the entire thing draws your eyes, showing a cake “Will you live with me”you turn and see Jin making a smug face. “How about it? You wouldn’t let all this hard work go to waste would you?” Instead of answering you stick your finger into the icing of the cake and smear it across Jin’s face, “Of course pabo!”


Suga-

Yoongi wasn’t sure how to ask you to move in with him, he wasn’t one to just blurt things like that out. He wanted it to be simple and sweet, mainly because he wanted to show you he cared a lot about you. It took some time for him to figure out exactly what he wanted to do, and a couple more days to get everything ready. You were simply comfortable in your own apartment watching a drama when you heard a knock on your door, answering it no one was there. You closed it, shrugging it off as someone who went to the wrong place. You were just about to start the drama up again, when another knock resonates. A bit annoyed you ignore it, opting to turn your drama up instead. The knock turns into full blown pounding on your door within minutes. Pissed off you stomp over to the door, revealing an equally annoyed Yoongi. “Yah! Open your door and pay attention next time would you!” He snaps. “Why are you banging on my door?!” he doesn’t answer, instead shuts your door and knocks again. Huffing you open the door and look down where keys were laying on the ground. You pick the up, when you stand back up Yoongi was in front of you. “You ruined my plan, but I guess this works.” He takes the keys from you and shakes them, “Move in with me?” You smirk, “Well since you asked so nicely, of course!”


J-Hope-

Hoseok wanted to move in with you right away, the two of you while haven’t been dating for a long time have a strong connection. This was one of the the reasons he was so quick to want to live with you, there wasn’t any special way he wanted to ask either. He came to your place with a bouquet of sunflowers and a smile full of love and hope. You opened the door before he could knock, since you yourself were about to go out to see him. “Hobi! I was just on my way to the dorm!” you pull him inside and shut the door. You eye the flowers and he quickly hands them over, “Is today special or something?” you inquire. He just shakes his head, smile still on his face. “I came over to ask you a very important question.” he gets down a knee. You eyes grow wide, “Hoseok, I um don’t think-” you stutter. “Will you move in with me? I got my own place now jagi!” he blurts out. You break out in giggles, “Did you even have to ask?” you laugh as you embrace him.   


RM-

He lost the keys. Namjoon didn’t even get a chance to think of how to ask you to move in with him, before the key to his new place vanished. He was pretty sure they were now broken somewhere. He called you over to meet in his studio to hang out for a bit, when you arrived you found him pouting in his seat. “You’re so cute, what’s wrong Joonie?” you squish his cheeks affectionately. “I was going to ask you to move in with me.” he brings you to him for a hug. “I can’t move into the dorm with you and the others.” you relax into him sighing. “No of course not, I got my own place Jagi.” he shakes his head pouting again. “But I lost the key I made you to ask.” You try to hold in laughter, and failed. “Yah! Are you laughing!” he laughs to. “Of course I’ll live with you, after all who else is going to keep you from destroying the place?”

V-

Taehyung planned to send Yeontan in with a note to ask you, since he knew how much you loved him. “Tae! What do you think about moving in together and getting a puppy friend for Yeontan?” you burst inside the dorm shouting. Out of shock, Taehyung throws the note he was writing and the pen across the room. “What was that.” you point in the direction of the things that flew. “Nothing, nothing. What were you saying about moving in together?” he waves it off as nothing. Shrugging you go to him excited, “I was saying that we should move in together, and maybe get another dog!?” You squeal. “Really? I was going to ask you the same thing!” you get louder and start jumping in excitement. The two of you were bouncing around happy, “Stop..” a tired Yoongi says from the doorway of his room. “Let’s go to our place.” Taehyung whispers in your ear. “Our place?” you whisper back as he pulls you out the dorm.


Jimin-

You’ve been asking Jimin if he just wanted to move in with you for a while now. Everything you asked though he would always reject your offer, which was a bit irritating, since he was over your place whenever he could. Jimin on the other hand was preparing his new place for your arrival, since he was that confident that you’d say yes to living with him when he asked. You were heading over to the address that jimin had texted you to meet him at, finding an apartment building. Going in and heading in the right direction you found Jimin waiting for you in front of the door you were planning on knocking on. “Come on!” he grabs your hand and pulls you inside the place. “Isn’t it nice, I got the guys to help with the setup. I’ve already got some of your clothes too.” He was speaking to fast for you to keep up. “W-what are you talking about.” he looks at you confused, probably as confused as you were. “Our place, well new home. Til we get married and get a house that is.” He was already looking forward to the future. “Is this why you kept turning down living with me?” your hands your on your hips. He nods still smiling. You couldn’t help but smile with him, “Fine.”


Jungkook-

Jungkook told Taehyung that he planned on moving out since he had found his own place, then Taehyung had told you since Jungkook was a bit shy. So he never asked you in a way, more like you invited yourself to live with him, without him knowing. You were in the process of putting your stuff away when he walks inside of the place. “Jagi! When did you get here, uh how did you know?” He starts blushing a bit avoiding eye contact. “Tae told me…sad I couldn’t hear it from my boyfriend Kookie.” You playfully roll your eyes. He tackle hugs you and starts to tickle your sides, “I’m sorry, I just didn’t know how to ask. Forgive me?” you could barely hear him over your shouts of mercy. “Fine! Fine please enough, I’ll pee myself.” he hops off when you say that, placing a sweet kiss on your forehead. He sits beside you as you catch your breath, “What should we do now?” he looks at you. “Well…we could break in the bed.” You wiggle your eyebrows. “Deal, last one there bottoms!” He yells as he was sprinting away.

He lost the keys. Namjoon didn’t even get a chance to think of how to ask you to move in with him, before the key to his new place vanished. He was pretty sure they were now broken somewhere. He called you over to meet in his studio to hang out for a bit, when you arrived you found him pouting in his seat. “You’re so cute, what’s wrong Joonie?” you squish his cheeks affectionately. “I was going to ask you to move in with me.” he brings you to him for a hug. “I can’t move into the dorm with you and the others.” you relax into him sighing. “No of course not, I got my own place Jagi.” he shakes his head pouting again. “But I lost the key I made you to ask.” You try to hold in laughter, and failed. “Yah! Are you laughing!” he laughs to. “Of course I’ll live with you, after all who else is going to keep you from destroying the place?”

[[MORE]]

V-

Taehyung planned to send Yeontan in with a note to ask you, since he knew how much you loved him. “Tae! What do you think about moving in together and getting a puppy friend for Yeontan?” you burst inside the dorm shouting. Out of shock, Taehyung throws the note he was writing and the pen across the room. “What was that.” you point in the direction of the things that flew. “Nothing, nothing. What were you saying about moving in together?” he waves it off as nothing. Shrugging you go to him excited, “I was saying that we should move in together, and maybe get another dog!?” You squeal. “Really? I was going to ask you the same thing!” you get louder and start jumping in excitement. The two of you were bouncing around happy, “Stop..” a tired Yoongi says from the doorway of his room. “Let’s go to our place.” Taehyung whispers in your ear. “Our place?” you whisper back as he pulls you out the dorm.


Jimin-

You’ve been asking Jimin if he just wanted to move in with you for a while now. Everything you asked though he would always reject your offer, which was a bit irritating, since he was over your place whenever he could. Jimin on the other hand was preparing his new place for your arrival, since he was that confident that you’d say yes to living with him when he asked. You were heading over to the address that jimin had texted you to meet him at, finding an apartment building. Going in and heading in the right direction you found Jimin waiting for you in front of the door you were planning on knocking on. “Come on!” he grabs your hand and pulls you inside the place. “Isn’t it nice, I got the guys to help with the setup. I’ve already got some of your clothes too.” He was speaking to fast for you to keep up. “W-what are you talking about.” he looks at you confused, probably as confused as you were. “Our place, well new home. Til we get married and get a house that is.” He was already looking forward to the future. “Is this why you kept turning down living with me?” your hands your on your hips. He nods still smiling. You couldn’t help but smile with him, “Fine.”


Jungkook-

Jungkook told Taehyung that he planned on moving out since he had found his own place, then Taehyung had told you since Jungkook was a bit shy. So he never asked you in a way, more like you invited yourself to live with him, without him knowing. You were in the process of putting your stuff away when he walks inside of the place. “Jagi! When did you get here, uh how did you know?” He starts blushing a bit avoiding eye contact. “Tae told me…sad I couldn’t hear it from my boyfriend Kookie.” You playfully roll your eyes. He tackle hugs you and starts to tickle your sides, “I’m sorry, I just didn’t know how to ask. Forgive me?” you could barely hear him over your shouts of mercy. “Fine! Fine please enough, I’ll pee myself.” he hops off when you say that, placing a sweet kiss on your forehead. He sits beside you as you catch your breath, “What should we do now?” he looks at you. “Well…we could break in the bed.” You wiggle your eyebrows. “Deal, last one there bottoms!” He yells as he was sprinting away.
trail.content:
*Note: Some may wonder why did it take so long if this isn’t long…well I don’t have an answer…or a schedule*

Jin-

Jin decided to move out of the dorm into his own apartment after the explosion of popularity with the group. He, of course being the oldest, wanted more space of his own. The two of you have been dating for more than a year now, coming on a strong second year of the relationship, and more than anything he wanted to share the space with you. “Jin, where are you taking me? Can I take off this blindfold now, this is a bit unnerving.” giggling you flail your arms out hoping not to bump into anything. “Where’s the trust Jagi?” he continues guiding you, where eventually he leads you to sit down. You feel his hands on your head and he restores your vision, blinking a couple of times you gasp at the dinner laid out for you. The centerpiece of the entire thing draws your eyes, showing a cake “Will you live with me”you turn and see Jin making a smug face. “How about it? You wouldn’t let all this hard work go to waste would you?” Instead of answering you stick your finger into the icing of the cake and smear it across Jin’s face, “Of course pabo!”

You closed it, shrugging it off as someone who went to the wrong place. You were just about to start the drama up again, when another knock resonates. A bit annoyed you ignore it, opting to turn your drama up instead. The knock turns into full blown pounding on your door within minutes. Pissed off you stomp over to the door, revealing an equally annoyed Yoongi. “Yah! Open your door and pay attention next time would you!” He snaps. “Why are you banging on my door?!” he doesn’t answer, instead shuts your door and knocks again. Huffing you open the door and look down where keys were laying on the ground. You pick the up, when you stand back up Yoongi was in front of you. “You ruined my plan, but I guess this works.” He takes the keys from you and shakes them, “Move in with me?” You smirk, “Well since you asked so nicely, of course!”


J-Hope-

He just shakes his head, smile still on his face. “I came over to ask you a very important question.” he gets down a knee. You eyes grow wide, “Hoseok, I um don’t think-” you stutter. “Will you move in with me? I got my own place now jagi!” he blurts out.
